<body>
  <div class="privacy-policy-container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>At our coffee shop, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Name, email, and message from contact form</li>
      <li>Order details including your name, item selected, and quantity</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used only to process orders and respond to contact messages. We do not sell, rent, or share
      your information with third parties.</p>

    <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies to improve your user experience on our website.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your information, but no website can guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h2>5. Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, contact us via the
      <a href="/#contact">contact form</a>.
    </p>

    <br>
    <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>

</html>